        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0669P0_20050222_GCR_74' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        5.45 p.m.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0669P0-03504'>
