      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0669P0-03540'>
        <a name='S5LV0669P0_20050222_GCR_111'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-alan-campbell-1' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0669P0_20050222_GCR_111' title='Link to this speech by Mr Alan Campbell' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
